slieb.kute.api

Interface Resource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContentResource, Resource.Readable, Resource.Writable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BytesArrayResource, CachedResource, FileResource, InputStreamResource, MutableBytesArrayResource, NamedResource, OutputStreamResource, RenamedPathResource, StringSupplierResource, URLResource

    public interface Resource
extends Serializable
    The Resource class represents a entry on the class path.

    Resources can also implement Resource.Readable or Resource.Writable

    Calling resource.getPath() will work on all resources.

      • getPath

        String getPath()
        The path the the given resource. This path is not to be confused with system path of the filesystem, even some overlap might exist. A resource exists within a Resource.Provider at its given path.
        Returns:
        The resource path.
